enb_long_title: Seventh Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
section_title: DRAFT DECISIONS FORWARDED FOR ELABORATION, COMPLETION AND ADOPTION
sentences: Draft decisions under the BAPA were forwarded from COP-6 Part II to COP-7 for further negotiation and completion on a number of key issues, including Protocol Articles 5, 7 and 8, LULUCF, the mechanisms, compliance, and policies and measures.
